          "ADD-RES": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "  Scattering cross-section were measured by",
                "transmission method (neutron energy 0.0047 eV) to be",
                "- for deuterium :",
                " SIGortho = 15.95+-0.03 b (even rotational quantum",
